{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "萧月仙与邵紫薇在山居练剑，遭一名手持判官笔的神秘人袭击，此人施展惊神笔法逼问缪长风下落。邵鹤年赶来救援但不敌。云紫萝暗中观察，认出对方使用的是连家绝技惊神笔法。杨牧与楚天雄带着石朝玑的手下找到云紫萝的山居，孟元超在门口以一敌三拼死守护。萧夫人与楚天雄激战，用腰带作软鞭对抗。庄鲲持锯齿刀攻入卧室欲抓云紫萝，被萧夫人梅花针击退。石朝玑亲自现身，以段仇世为人质要挟，声称华儿已平安送到京城。双方陷入混战，云紫萝最终从后门带众人撤离。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "speaker_name": "萧月仙",
      "listener": "char_shao_zi_wei",
      "text": "难得这样的好天气，邵姐姐，咱们来练剑吧。",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_zi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "邵紫薇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "text": "好呀，只是紫萝也是奇怪，这样的好天气，她却躲在房里不肯出来。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "speaker_name": "萧月仙",
      "listener": "char_shao_zi_wei",
      "text": "她有身孕，身子不便，由她安静歇息吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼？我说你们不知天高地厚，没有说错你们吧？不过你们两个人我却不知要带走哪个，倒是有点为难了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_zi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "邵紫薇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，有人欺负女儿，你快来呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "speaker_name": "萧月仙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈妈快来帮我！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫爹叫娘也没用，除非你们把缪长风的行踪老老实实的告诉我，否则我一定要把你们一个带走，着落在你们的身上，非把缪长风逼出来不可，小姑娘你说不说？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "speaker_name": "萧月仙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放你的屁，你要我们卖友求饶，那是休想！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，你这丫头嘴刁，我要你非说不可，跟我走吧！",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_he_nian",
      "speaker_name": "邵鹤年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欺侮女子，算得什么好汉！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_zi_wei",
      "speaker_name": "邵鹤年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你来了，小心，小心！留神他的点穴！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_shao_he_nian",
      "text": "好，你跑来充当好汉，我倒要看你有什么本领？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_kun",
      "text": "你敢伤我女儿一根毫发，我必定取你性命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "楚天雄",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_kun",
      "text": "庄鲲你别怕她，她是泥菩萨过江，自身难保！",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "楚天雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_furen",
      "text": "萧夫人，你要保全女儿，那只有赶早抽身，别沾浑水！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "text": "且看谁是泥菩萨过江。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_chao_ji",
      "speaker_name": "石朝玑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有救兵，我也早有理伏，不用担忧，今日我担保可以令你手刃仇人就是！",
      "tone": "喜悦",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孟某只有一条性命，你们哪个想要，尽管来吧！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "楚天雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_furen",
      "text": "萧夫人果然不愧女中豪杰，小老儿向夫人请教请教。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "云紫萝是你表姐吧，你只须和陈公子疏远一些，我担保他不会再来纠缠你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_si_mei",
      "speaker_name": "吕思美",
      "listener": "char_song_teng_xiao",
      "text": "你和紫薇是不是为了他吵架？你的邵家哥哥又是不是为了这个给你气跑的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "text": "你放什么臭屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_chao_ji",
      "speaker_name": "石朝玑",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "我们也不能和你客气了，捉住了冷面书生段仇世，华儿已经平安送到京城了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我得韩威武之助，还是抱病在身，我早就忘了，我拗不过你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "这姓孟的与你非亲非故，你来得正好，你太多疑了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "speaker_name": "萧月仙",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "陈大哥此问定有用意，你们还是继续练剑吧，待我进去把她唤出来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "楚天雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕你不但保不了外人，连你的女儿也保不了。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_furen",
      "speaker_name": "萧夫人",
      "listener": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "text": "我们也不能和你客气了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_mu",
      "speaker_name": "杨牧",
      "listener": "char_chu_tian_xiong",
      "text": "多让他们亲近，你可别要多心。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "石朝玑",
      "listener": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "text": "你只须和陈公子疏远一些，这样做太着痕迹了，那会闹出笑话来的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "speaker_name": "萧月仙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这孩子哪里来的，我说的不是这个，由我陪客人回家。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_yuan_chao",
      "speaker_name": "孟元超",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孟元超势如疯虎，我何苦和他拼命。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_xian",
      "text": "你偷听了他们的一些什么秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38
    }
  ],
